Real Estate in zip code 01778

Housing occupied 95.6% Housing vacant 4.4% Housing occupied by owner 88.83% Housing occupied by tenant 11.17% Total Rented Units 559 Median Contract Gross Rent $896 Median Gross Rent $1,019 Median Home Value $603,700

Contract rent is the monthly cash rent agreed to, regardless of any furnishings, utilities, fees, meals, or services that may be included. Gross rent is the contract rent plus the estimated average monthly cost of utilities and fuels if these are paid by the renter. In zip code 01778 median gross rent is 13.73% larger then the median contract rent.
